  "title": "Loading Master (Shift, Onboard)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Based on-board Floating Storage Unit as a Loading Master.</li>\n  <li>Handle cargo transfer operations according to cargo transfer plan to ensure operations are carried out in a timely and efficient manner.</li>\n  <li>Perform cargo inspections and monitor vessel operations to ensure that all operations are compliant with the regulatory system and recognised industry codes of practice.</li>\n  <li>Maintain necessary and accurate cargo transfer documentations (including full set of Bill of Lading documents, discharge certificate, time log etc) and report to head office accordingly.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma and above</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of experience as a Loading Master.</li>\n  <li>Able to <strong>perform shift</strong> and <strong>stay onboard</strong> vessel.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
